        <p>This is to certify that <strong>${e.employeeName}</strong>, with Employee No. <strong>${e.employeeNo}</strong>, from the <strong>${e.department}</strong> department, has officially appeared and reported for duty/travel to <strong>${e.destination}</strong> from <strong>${e.dateFrom}</strong> to <strong>${e.dateTo}</strong>, covering a period of <strong>${e.days} day(s)</strong>.</p>
        
